<view class="weather-page">
  <view class="sky-hero">
    <text class="kicker">爱木长诗 · 双人天气卡</text>
    <text class="title">天气卡片</text>
    <text class="subtitle">可以看自己的天气，也可以看 Ta 主动同步的位置。真实天气由云函数获取，API key 不会出现在前端。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="state-card" wx:if="{{bindingState==='loading'}}">
    <text>正在确认绑定状态</text>
    <text>{{bindingMessage}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="state-card" wx:elif="{{!bindingReady}}">
    <text>请先绑定情侣关系</text>
    <text>{{bindingMessage}}</text>
  </view>

  <block wx:else>
    <view class="remote-card loading-card" wx:if="{{loading}}">
      <text class="waiting-title">正在看你们两边的天空</text>
      <text class="waiting-text">如果天气服务慢一点，这里会温柔地等一会儿。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="weather-grid" wx:else>
      <view class="remote-card self-card" wx:if="{{myWeather}}">
        <text class="card-label">我的天气</text>
        <view class="remote-top">
          <view>
            <text class="city">{{myWeather.city}}</text>
            <text class="updated">天气更新时间 {{myWeather.updatedText || '刚刚'}}</text>
          </view>
          <view class="temp">{{myWeather.temp}}°</view>
        </view>
        <view class="weather-line">
          <text>{{myWeather.condition}}</text>
          <text>体感 {{myWeather.feelsLike}}°</text>
          <text wx:if="{{myWeather.humidity}}">湿度 {{myWeather.humidity}}%</text>
          <text wx:if="{{myWeather.weatherCode || myWeather.weatherCode === 0}}">代码 {{myWeather.weatherCode}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="weather-detail">
          <text wx:if="{{myWeather.windSpeed}}">风速：{{myWeather.windSpeed}} km/h</text>
          <text wx:if="{{myWeather.windDir}}">风向：{{myWeather.windDir}}</text>
          <text wx:if="{{myWeather.windScale}}">风力：{{myWeather.windScale}}级</text>
        </view>
        <text class="care-tip">{{myWeather.tip}}</text>
        <text class="api-note" wx:if="{{myConfigMissing}}">天气服务暂未配置。默认 Open-Meteo 不需要 key；只有切到 QWeather 时才需要配置 key。</text>
      </view>

      <view class="waiting-card compact" wx:else>
        <text class="card-label">我的天气</text>
        <text class="waiting-title">{{myWaitingText}}</text>
        <text class="waiting-text">Open-Meteo 需要经纬度。点“用当前位置”或直接点“同步我的天气位置”，都会尝试获取经纬度。</text>
      </view>

      <view class="remote-card partner-card" wx:if="{{partnerWeather}}">
        <text class="card-label">Ta 的天气</text>
        <view class="remote-top">
          <view>
            <text class="city">{{partnerWeather.city}}</text>
            <text class="updated">天气更新时间 {{partnerWeather.updatedText || '刚刚'}}</text>
          </view>
          <view class="temp">{{partnerWeather.temp}}°</view>
        </view>
        <view class="weather-line">
          <text>{{partnerWeather.condition}}</text>
          <text>体感 {{partnerWeather.feelsLike}}°</text>
          <text wx:if="{{partnerWeather.humidity}}">湿度 {{partnerWeather.humidity}}%</text>
          <text wx:if="{{partnerWeather.weatherCode || partnerWeather.weatherCode === 0}}">代码 {{partnerWeather.weatherCode}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="weather-detail">
          <text wx:if="{{partnerWeather.windSpeed}}">风速：{{partnerWeather.windSpeed}} km/h</text>
          <text wx:if="{{partnerWeather.windDir}}">风向：{{partnerWeather.windDir}}</text>
          <text wx:if="{{partnerWeather.windScale}}">风力：{{partnerWeather.windScale}}级</text>
        </view>
        <text class="care-tip">{{partnerWeather.tip}}</text>
        <text class="api-note" wx:if="{{partnerConfigMissing}}">天气服务暂未配置。默认 Open-Meteo 不需要 key；只有切到 QWeather 时才需要配置 key。</text>
      </view>

      <view class="waiting-card compact" wx:else>
        <text class="card-label">Ta 的天气</text>
        <text class="waiting-title">{{waitingText}}</text>
        <text class="waiting-text">不能偷偷获取对方定位。需要 Ta 主动授权选择位置，或手动填写城市后同步。</text>
        <button bindtap="retryWeather">刷新看看</button>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="sync-card">
      <text class="section-title">把我的位置同步给 Ta</text>
      <text class="privacy">Open-Meteo 需要经纬度，建议先点“用当前位置”；地图选点打不开时也不影响同步天气。</text>
      <view class="city-row">
        <input placeholder="手动填写城市或地点" value="{{cityInput}}" bindinput="onCityInput" maxlength="40" />
      </view>
      <view class="location-actions">
        <button bindtap="useCurrentLocation">用当前位置</button>
        <button class="ghost" bindtap="chooseMyLocation">地图选点</button>
      </view>
      <button class="sync-btn" bindtap="saveMyLocation" loading="{{saving}}">同步我的天气位置</button>
      <text class="mine" wx:if="{{myCity}}">我已同步：{{myCity}} {{myUpdatedText}}</text>
      <text class="mine ok" wx:if="{{hasMyCoordinates}}">已保存经纬度：{{myCoordinateText}}</text>
      <text class="mine warn" wx:elif="{{myCity}}">这条记录还缺少经纬度，请重新点“用当前位置”或“同步我的天气位置”。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="error" wx:if="{{errorMessage}}">
      <text>{{errorMessage}}</text>
      <button bindtap="retryWeather">重试</button>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
